---
title: Peruvian-Style Chicken with Potato Coins and Cilantro-Jalapeño Sauce
description: Tonight, everyday chicken breasts get a flavourful makeover! Garlic puree and aromatic spices make a bold rub for tender, roasted chicken. Dunk it into the bright cilantro-jalapeño sauce, inspired by Peruvian 'Aji Verde', for a taste explosion!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/peruvian-style-chicken-f1092658.jpg
